dct_title_s: Carte administrative de la Turquie d'Europe et de la Turquie d'Asie (Asia Minor)
dct_description_sm: Map of Turkey and the Balkan Peninsula; relief shown by hachures. Inset: Moutessarifat du Liban. The political boundaries show the Ottoman Empire after Bulgarian independence in 1908, but before the outbreak of the Balkan Wars of 1912-1913.
